{"tid":182794,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求各位巴絲打聽一聽小弟既往事評下理","createTime":"2017-04-01T14:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T14:25:48.000Z","uid":98542,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6c04376cbf05267c6abb12373485d8ceaff2fb7c","tid":182794,"uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T14:58:21.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟以前去過一間位於北角<br />\n叫Smart Workshop既補習社<br />\n嗰間野唔係D咩大型補習社<br />\n只係得一個叫鄧莊萍既女人坐陣<br />\n佢原本係我老豆個舊同事嚟<br />\n自己開咗間補習社<br />\n<br />\n你第一次入到去<br />\n你會覺得個女人對你好nice<br />\n而且感覺個補習社好有歸屬感<br />\n因為你可以係嗰度食飯又得<br />\n做功課又得、吹水又得<br />\n得閑又會成班學生出去行街食飯<br />\n好似好正咁<br />\n但呢個只係惡夢既開始<br />\n<br />\n個女人之後會開始同你洗腦<br />\n話你個樣好黑<br />\n係俾魔鬼控制<br />\n又成日講好多甚麼鬼上身、驅魔之類既東西<br />\n話咩自己靈性好強、係神差遣既使者<br />\n連魔鬼都怕咗佢<br />\n然後叫你祈禱，同神悔改<br />\n再搵埋其他學生用群眾壓力嚟迫你信神<br />\n又話唔信既話我父母會死得好慘<br />\n嗰陣十三歲，咩都唔知<br />\n咁咪信囉<br />\n<br />\n仆街，個女人之後要我去佢嗰D咩查經班<br />\n得閑係補習社又會話你聽緊魔鬼講野<br />\n然後佢又搵埋其他學生一齊屌尻你<br />\n又用聖經金句撻我<br />\n嗰陣答又死，唔答又死<br />\n就連諗野都會話你<br />\n我嗰陣連喊都唔敢喊<br />\n但佢又唔會叫我番教會<br />\n又成日鬧D教會有靈恩有邪氣<br />\n聽聞佢仲辣㷫過幾間大教會(e.g. 北角衛理)<br />\n<br />\n平時冇事嗰陣我自己又會好驚自己「聽魔鬼講野」<br />\n不斷祈禱、不斷睇聖經<br />\n到我中三嗰陣<br />\n已經將新約聖經睇過兩次<br />\n連書都唔讀就走去讀聖經，睇靈修書<br />\n之後成績差又俾個八婆屌<br />\n話我連做人資格都冇<br />\n<br />\n後尾有次佢同班學生因為我個message「似機械人講野」又俾佢地屌一餐<br />\n我老豆老母發現咗佢地係度批鬥我<br />\n即刻停咗我唔俾我再去呢間補習社<br />\n之後我開始周不時情緒失控<br />\n又成日好驚咁<br />\n去精神科睇發現我有抑鬱同焦慮<br />\n仲有自殺傾向<br />\n次次一諗番起佢地我又會失控<br />\n好想自殺<br />\n有次試過入埋精神病院<br />\n<br />\n我其實勁辛苦先講到呢單野出嚟<br />\n甚至我都唔想出呢段野出街<br />\n我好驚嗰班人會嚟搵我<br />\n但我知道我隨時會自殺<br />\n我一自殺，呢單野就冇人知<br />\n希望各位巴打絲打們<br />\n特別住北角嗰頭既各位<br />\n小心呢個巫婆<br />\n佢唔係基督徒嚟<br />\n佢係邪教徒＋癲婆一條<br />\n佢害過我既野<br />\n我呢一世都唔會忘記<br />\n<br />\n之後你地若果想知更多<br />\n我會再po埋出嚟"},{"pid":"e98655102c5091c16f228633f8bf1adb8a04a7ed","tid":182794,"uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T15:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/01/230146_82457bfe4c8ce4b2cbbc3769195252b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F01%2F230146_82457bfe4c8ce4b2cbbc3769195252b1.jpg&h=68cec5b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9w4zs4x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9w4zs4x.jpg&h=8d0d579c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Q46byV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Q46byV.jpg&h=d486d708&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B3N10w0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB3N10w0.jpg&h=0690890e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/01/230148_62d212157dd692b0976b7fb0b657f6ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F01%2F230148_62d212157dd692b0976b7fb0b657f6ec.jpg&h=1da1bb84&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/01/230206_ab5db386bf1c0bf19f7c143817df4324.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F01%2F230206_ab5db386bf1c0bf19f7c143817df4324.jpg&h=921a9b35&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FAs5y0g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFAs5y0g.jpg&h=787433c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TcwZn18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTcwZn18.jpg&h=b2af038f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W589k5n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW589k5n.jpg&h=c4ec7649&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7X24eq2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7X24eq2.jpg&h=bf736217&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LQHg0Y3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLQHg0Y3.jpg&h=182e5fce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/01/230226_802c7e71f2cc96455504a03a913acd28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F01%2F230226_802c7e71f2cc96455504a03a913acd28.jpg&h=9c38e49a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hwa92q6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHwa92q6.jpg&h=c875ad54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"219496b0d8e9a92b039e988dfc6d53660cc11155","tid":182794,"uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T15:03:32.000Z","msg":"呢D就係佢地講過既野<br />\nMoses=小弟"},{"pid":"5c3b124af43bbcc42c52e55455618204b559f7e3","tid":182794,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T15:04:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6c9ff09b25b67eaa200c680aa2f12c548785ea8","tid":182794,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T15:11:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62517e37a12c24d77858238f39475225b019e02a","tid":182794,"uid":79567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T15:32:50.000Z","msg":"呢啲真係用信仰cover自己真係痴線嘅人"},{"pid":"e0509ba35cac8a78de39105a438a3156904f1bd6","tid":182794,"uid":9749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T07:37:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0933d3c5223bfeb1feecdcf88f31b254bba4cfa1","tid":182794,"uid":93492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:42:19.000Z","msg":"認真聽緊，巴打有冇信得過既人可以傾訢？"},{"pid":"8f47dacbb1f93121381b447994de1cda0d62a4af","tid":182794,"uid":54175,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:29:42.000Z","msg":"好撚痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留咗名先，依家要溫書，4個鐘後考試<br />\n之後詳細再睇"},